org.openmobster.core.mobileCloud.api.javascript
Class MobileBeanBridge

java.lang.Object
  org.openmobster.core.mobileCloud.api.javascript.MobileBeanBridge

public final class MobileBeanBridge
extends Object

A Javascript bridge that exposes the OpenMobster MobileBean service to the HTML5/Javascript layer of the App. This is just a prototypical bridge. A more standardized OpenMobster Javascript API will be finalized in the 2.2 release cycle This bridge only exposes functionality necessary by the simple tutorial App

Author:
openmobster@gmail.com
